import React from 'react' import { GlobalStyle, Info, Text } from '../Styles/Styles' import { useParams } from 'react-router-dom' import ListBooks from '../Data/ListBooks' import Book from '../Components/Book' const BookDetail = _ => { let { id } = useParams(); return (

Title: { ListBooks[id].title }

Pages: { ListBooks[id].pages }

Price: { ListBooks[id].price }

Release date of: { ListBooks[id].Release_date_of }

Publishing: { ListBooks[id].publishing }

Units: { ListBooks[id].units }

) } export default BookDetail
